query:
SELECT indicatorCode, regimeTag, COUNT(*) as count, MIN(date) as earliest, MAX(date) as latest 
FROM time_series 
WHERE indicatorCode LIKE '%fx%' OR indicatorCode LIKE '%exchange%' OR indicatorCode LIKE '%rate%'
GROUP BY indicatorCode, regimeTag
ORDER BY indicatorCode, regimeTag;
